        <abstract>
            <p>Has received a baffling article on God, immortality, and socialism under a Darwinian point of view.</p> 
<p>Clerk Maxwell has disagreed with CD on molecular calculations in relation to Pangenesis in <hi rend="italic">Encyclopaedia Britannica</hi> article ["Atom", <hi rend="italic">Encyclopaedia Britannica</hi>, 9th ed. (1875) 3: 36–49].</p> 
